name: HERE  RECTION / HER E RECTION / HER  ERECTION
description: And now for some adult humor, sorry kids, this boomerang letter group is NOT for you. In my work, I only use real words. It might look like gibberish, but there's a reason for all of it. Sometimes there is absolutely no narrative whatsoever, sometimes there is. In this case, HERE is sharing some "E" (slang for Ecstacy, or MDMA, a drug popular in clubs) with RECTION (the influence or power of a word in consequence of which another word in the sentence must have a certain form, in regard to number, case, person, mode, or the like; government.). She's taken the drug (which one of the side effect are increase in libido for many who consume it) and now well...she's uhhhh...ready to go. (end scene)
